{"tid":1216723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明日會議又取消！","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:51:27.000Z","uid":258448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51e1df477e246760146e84b2db17e3c314e5e453","tid":1216723,"uid":258448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/立法會明日不開大會-一連三日取消會議/?fbclid=IwAR1I38rTmha2Bu436PzJHQH2tC0SffGghOooJQGpIxV9RUUoZEajbOVrheg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%80%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1I38rTmha2Bu436PzJHQH2tC0SffGghOooJQGpIxV9RUUoZEajbOVrheg&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=ebb4ddca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%80%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1I38rTmha2Bu436PzJHQH2tC0SffGghOooJQGpIxV9RUUoZEajbOVrheg&h=20956828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/立法會明日不開大會-一連三日取消會議/?fbclid=IwAR1I38rTmha2Bu436PzJHQH2tC0SffGghOooJQGpIxV9RUUoZEajbOVrheg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書處今日傍通知議員，立法會大會明日繼續不召開會議，暫時無法恢復二讀逃犯條例修訂。<br />\n<br />\n立法會大會原本在昨日（6月12日）恢復二讀逃犯條例修訂，但反送中運動演變成佔領金鐘，警方不斷使用暴力驅趕民眾，最終昨天和今日的會議都取消，連同明日大會取消，亦即一連三日會議取消。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥暫時未通知議員，何時會恢複大會。<br />\n<br />\n主席梁君彥原本宣布預留會議共61小時審議，並在本周五、下周一和二加會，料下周四（20日）表決草案。"}]}